snippet.title: The Sieged City | Season 6 Cinematic Trailer - Arena Breakout
snippet.description:
Renoir is the mastermind, orchestrating the moves while others remain under the illusion of being in control. Here, he introduces brand new features in Season 6：

1️⃣ STORY MISSION
2️⃣ NORTHRIDGE ROYALE
3️⃣ THE FOBBIDEN ZONE
4️⃣ RENOIR‘S OUTFIT

More features will be revealed for Season 6 on October 11th on iOS and Android! http://bit.ly/3Jel2aJ   

#ArenaBreakoutS6 #OperationBlackout
